    "id": 1,
    "year": 2013,
    "type": "论述题",
    "question": "麻花钻的结构特点及工作特点",
    "answer": "<span style='background:#f0f9ff; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>麻花钻的工作特点：</span><span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>麻花钻工作部分的前端为切削部分</span>，承担主要的切削工作，<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>后端为导向部分</span>，起引导钻头的作用，也是切削部分的最后部分。工作部分有<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>两个对称的刃瓣</span>（通过中间的钻芯连接在一起），<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>两条对称的螺旋槽</span>（用于容屑和排屑）；导向部分磨有<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>两条棱边</span>（刃带），为了减少与加工孔壁的摩擦，<span style='background:#f472b6; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>棱边直径磨有倒锥量</span>。\n\n<span style='background:#f0f9ff; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>结构特点：</span><span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>麻花钻的两个刃瓣可以看作两把对称的车刀</span>；<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>螺旋槽的螺旋面为前刀面</span>，与工件过渡表面相对的端部两面为<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>主后刀面</span>。与工件的加工表面相对的两条棱边为<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>副后刀面</span>，<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>螺旋槽与主后刀面的两条交线为主切削刃</span>，<span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>棱边与螺旋槽的两条交线为副切削刃</span>。麻花钻的<span style='background:#f472b6; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>横刃为前后刀面在钻芯处的交线</span>。",
    "tags": ["麻花钻", "刀具", "切削"],
    "memoryTips": "<div style='background:#f0f9ff; padding:15px; border-radius:12px; border-left:4px solid #0ea5e9;'><h4 style='color:#0369a1; margin-bottom:10px;'>答案解析</h4><div style='background:#e0f2fe; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0;'><p style='color:#0c4a6e; margin:0; line-height:1.8;'><strong>为什么这样答？</strong> 题目要求回答<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>工作特点</span>和<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>结构特点</span>两部分，需要分别阐述。</p></div><img src='images/twist-drill.svg' style='max-width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:2px solid #0ea5e9;' alt='麻花钻结构图'/><h5 style='color:#0369a1; margin:15px 0 8px;'>工作特点记忆要点</h5><ul style='color:#334155; margin:0; padding-left:20px; line-height:2;'><li><span style='background:#dcfce7; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>前端</span>是<span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>切削部分</span>（干活的地方）</li><li><span style='background:#dcfce7; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>后端</span>是<span style='background:#93c5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>导向部分</span>（引导方向）</li><li>两条<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>螺旋槽</span>用于<span style='background:#fde047; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>容屑和排屑</span></li><li>两条<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>棱边</span>（刃带）有<span style='background:#f472b6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>倒锥量</span>（减少摩擦）</li></ul><h5 style='color:#0369a1; margin:15px 0 8px;'>结构特点记忆要点</h5><p style='color:#334155; margin:0 0 10px;'>把麻花钻想象成<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>两把对称的车刀</span>，然后分析各面、各刃：</p><table style='width:100%; margin:10px 0; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px;'><tr style='background:#e0f2fe;'><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #7dd3fc;'>要素</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #7dd3fc;'>对应部位</th></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>前刀面</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'>螺旋槽的螺旋面</td></tr><tr style='background:#f0f9ff;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>主后刀面</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'>与过渡表面相对的端部两面</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>副后刀面</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'>两条棱边</td></tr><tr style='background:#f0f9ff;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>主切削刃</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'>螺旋槽与主后刀面的交线</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>副切削刃</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'>棱边与螺旋槽的交线</td></tr><tr style='background:#f0f9ff;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>横刃</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #bae6fd;'>前后刀面在钻芯处的交线</td></tr></table></div>"
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "year": 2013,
    "type": "论述题",
    "question": "磨削、珩磨、研磨、抛光的区别",
    "answer": "<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>磨削：</span>通过<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>砂轮高速旋转</span>，砂轮上的<span style='background:#fde047; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>磨粒刻划</span>被加工表面来加工以<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>提高工件表面质量</span>。\n\n<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>珩磨：</span>利用<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>磨条</span>以<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>一定的压力</span>压在工件的被加工表面上，并相对工件作<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>旋转与往复运动</span>以<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>降低工件粗糙度，提高精度</span>。\n\n<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>研磨：</span>将<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>研磨剂</span>涂敷或浇注在<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>研具与工件</span>间，工件与夹具在<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>一定压力</span>下作<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>不断变更方向的相对运动</span>，在磨粒的作用下<span style='background:#f472b6; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>逐步刮擦并微显切除工件表面的很薄的金属层</span>。\n\n<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>抛光：</span>利用<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>布轮、布盘等软的研具</span>涂上<span style='background:#f472b6; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>抛光膏</span>抛光工件表面，靠<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>抛光膏的机械刮擦与化学作用</span><span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>去掉粗糙度的峰顶</span>，使表面<span style='background:#3b82f6; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px; color:white;'>获得光泽镜面</span>。",
    "tags": ["磨削", "珩磨", "研磨", "抛光", "加工方法"],
    "memoryTips": "<div style='background:#fef3c7; padding:15px; border-radius:12px; border-left:4px solid #f59e0b;'><h4 style='color:#92400e; margin-bottom:10px;'>答案解析</h4><div style='background:#fde68a; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0;'><p style='color:#78350f; margin:0; line-height:1.8;'><strong>为什么这样答？</strong> 区别题需要从<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>加工工具</span>、<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>加工方式</span>、<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>加工目的</span>三个维度对比。</p></div><img src='images/grinding-comparison.svg' style='max-width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:2px solid #f59e0b;' alt='磨削珩磨研磨抛光对比图'/><table style='width:100%; margin:15px 0; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px;'><tr style='background:#fde68a;'><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f59e0b;'>方法</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f59e0b;'>核心工具</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f59e0b;'>关键动作</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f59e0b;'>主要目的</th></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>磨削</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'><span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>砂轮</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'>高速旋转+磨粒刻划</td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>提高表面质量</span></td></tr><tr style='background:#fffbeb;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>珩磨</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'><span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>磨条/油石</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'>旋转+往复运动</td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid:#fcd34d;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>降低粗糙度、提高精度</span></td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>研磨</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid:#fcd34d;'><span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>研具+研磨剂</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'>变更方向的相对运动</td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>微量切除（很薄的金属层）</span></td></tr><tr style='background:#fffbeb;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>抛光</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'><span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>布轮/布盘+抛光膏</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'>机械刮擦+化学作用</td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fcd34d;'><span style='background:#f472b6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>去掉峰顶-光泽镜面</span></td></tr></table><div style='background:#fef3c7; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:1px dashed #f59e0b;'><p style='color:#78350f; margin:0;'><strong>记忆逻辑：</strong>按精度从低到高排列：<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>磨削（粗）</span> <span style='background:#93c5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>珩磨（精）</span> <span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>研磨（超精）</span> <span style='background:#3b82f6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold; color:white;'>抛光（镜面）</span></p></div></div>"
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "year": 2013,
    "type": "论述题",
    "question": "加工工作平台T型槽的方法(机床及刀具)",
    "answer": "1. <span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>先按照所需尺寸划线做基准</span>。\n2. <span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>用比所需 T 型槽小的铣刀</span>铣到所需的深度。\n3. <span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>再用所需 T 型槽开口同样大的铣刀</span>铣到所需的深度。\n4. <span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>最后用所需开口同样大的 T 型铣刀</span>铣完即可。",
    "tags": ["T型槽", "铣削", "加工工艺"],
    "memoryTips": "<div style='background:#ecfdf5; padding:15px; border-radius:12px; border-left:4px solid #10b981;'><h4 style='color:#047857; margin-bottom:10px;'>答案解析</h4><div style='background:#d1fae5; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0;'><p style='color:#064e3b; margin:0; line-height:1.8;'><strong>为什么这样答？</strong> T型槽是<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>上宽下窄</span>的结构，无法一次成型，必须<span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>分步加工</span>。</p></div><img src='images/t-slot-machining.svg' style='max-width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:2px solid #10b981;' alt='T型槽加工方法图'/><h5 style='color:#047857; margin:15px 0 8px;'>四步加工逻辑</h5><ol style='color:#334155; margin:0; padding-left:20px; line-height:2;'><li><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>划线定位</span> - 先确定位置和尺寸基准</li><li><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>小铣刀开槽</span> - 用比目标<span style='background:#fde047; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>小</span>的铣刀铣到深度（预留余量）</li><li><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>等宽铣刀扩槽</span> - 用与开口<span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>等宽</span>的铣刀加工上部直槽</li><li><span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>T型铣刀成型</span> - 用T型铣刀铣削底部扩宽，形成T型结构</li></ol><div style='background:#d1fae5; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0;'><h5 style='color:#065f46; margin:0 0 8px;'>T型槽截面示意</h5><pre style='color:#064e3b; margin:0; font-family:monospace; font-size:14px; line-height:1.4;'>[=========]\n[         ] <- 直槽(立铣刀)\n[    +----+] \n[    |     ] <- 底槽(T型铣刀)\n[====     ]</pre></div><div style='background:#ecfdf5; padding:10px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0; border:1px dashed #10b981;'><p style='color:#065f46; margin:0;'><strong>核心思路：</strong><span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>先小后大，先直后T，逐步成型</span></p></div></div>"
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "year": 2013,
    "type": "论述题",
    "question": "误差复映及避免方法",
    "answer": "<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>误差复映：</span><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>毛坯的误差部分或全部复映到工件上的现象</span>。<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>由于毛坯加工余量和材料硬度的变化</span>，在加工过程中引起了<span style='background:#fde047; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>切削力的变化</span>，进而引起了<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>工艺系统受力变化的改变</span>。产生了工件的<span style='background:#f472b6; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>尺寸误差和形状误差</span>。<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>提高工艺系统的刚度</span>可减小或避免误差复映。",
    "tags": ["误差复映", "工艺系统", "加工精度"],
    "memoryTips": "<div style='background:#ede9fe; padding:15px; border-radius:12px; border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;'><h4 style='color:#5b21b6; margin-bottom:10px;'>答案解析</h4><div style='background:#ddd6fe; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0;'><p style='color:#4c1d95; margin:0; line-height:1.8;'><strong>为什么这样答？</strong> 需要解释<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>什么是误差复映</span>、<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>产生原因</span>、<span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>如何避免</span>三个层次。</p></div><img src='images/error-propagation.svg' style='max-width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:2px solid #8b5cf6;' alt='误差复映原理图'/><h5 style='color:#5b21b6; margin:15px 0 8px;'>误差复映的因果链</h5><div style='background:#f5f3ff; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0;'><p style='color:#4c1d95; margin:0; font-family:monospace; font-size:13px; line-height:2;'>1. <span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>毛坯误差</span> (余量不均/硬度变化)<br>2. <span style='background:#fde047; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>切削力变化</span><br>3. <span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>工艺系统变形</span><br>4. <span style='background:#f472b6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>工件误差</span> (复映)</p></div><h5 style='color:#5b21b6; margin:15px 0 8px;'>答案关键词</h5><ul style='color:#334155; margin:0; padding-left:20px; line-height:2;'><li><span style='background:#dcfce7; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>毛坯误差</span>：<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>余量和硬度变化</span>是根源</li><li><span style='background:#dcfce7; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>切削力变化</span>：导致<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>系统受力</span>的变化</li><li><span style='background:#dcfce7; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>工艺系统变形</span>：<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>误差传递</span>的中间环节</li><li><span style='background:#dcfce7; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>尺寸误差和形状误差</span>：最终<span style='background:#f472b6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>表现结果</span></li></ul><div style='background:#ede9fe; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:1px dashed #8b5cf6;'><p style='color:#5b21b6; margin:0;'><strong>避免方法核心：</strong><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>提高工艺系统刚度</span>（减少变形）是根本解决之道</p></div></div>"
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "year": 2014,
    "type": "词语解释",
    "question": "积屑瘤",
    "answer": "<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>积屑瘤：</span><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>在切削速度不高又能形成连续切削的情况下</span>常在<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>刀具前刀面</span>粘着一块<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>前面有时呈三角状的硬块</span>，在处于比较稳定的状态时能够<span style='background:#f472b6; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>代替切削力进行切削</span>。这块<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>冷焊在前刀面上的金属</span>称为积屑瘤。",
    "tags": ["积屑瘤", "切削", "刀具"],
    "memoryTips": "<div style='background:#fee2e2; padding:15px; border-radius:12px; border-left:4px solid #ef4444;'><h4 style='color:#991b1b; margin-bottom:10px;'>答案解析</h4><div style='background:#fecaca; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0;'><p style='color:#7f1d1d; margin:0; line-height:1.8;'><strong>为什么这样答？</strong> 词语解释需要包含<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>形成条件</span>、<span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>位置</span>、<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>形态</span>、<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>作用</span>、<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>本质</span>五个要素。</p></div><img src='images/built-up-edge.svg' style='max-width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:2px solid #ef4444;' alt='积屑瘤示意图'/><h5 style='color:#991b1b; margin:15px 0 8px;'>答案结构拆解</h5><table style='width:100%; margin:10px 0; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px;'><tr style='background:#fecaca;'><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f87171;'>要素</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f87171;'>答案关键词</th></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fca5a5;'><span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>形成条件</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fca5a5;'><span style='background:#fde047; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>切削速度不高</span> + <span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>连续切削</span></td></tr><tr style='background:#fef2f2;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fca5a5;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>位置</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fca5a5;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>刀具前刀面</span></td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fca5a5;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>形态</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fca5a5;'><span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>三角状硬块</span></td></tr><tr style='background:#fef2f2;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fca5a5;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>作用</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fca5a5;'><span style='background:#f472b6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>代替切削刃进行切削</span></td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid;#fca5a5;'><span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>本质</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #fca5a5;'><span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>冷焊在前刀面上的金属</span></td></tr></table><div style='background:#fee2e2; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:1px dashed #ef4444;'><p style='color:#991b1b; margin:0;'><strong>记忆要点：</strong>积屑瘤= <span style='background:#fde047; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>低速</span> + <span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>连续切削</span> + <span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>前刀面</span> + <span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>冷焊金属块</span></p></div></div>"
  },
  {
    "id": 6,
    "year": 2014,
    "type": "词语解释",
    "question": "削边销",
    "answer": "<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>削边销：</span><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>两孔定位</span>中，为了<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>增强两孔连心线方向上的间隙</span>，<span style='background:#ef4444; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>避免过定位</span>将<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>第二副碰到孔壁的部分削去</span>，<span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>只留下下一部分圆柱面</span>。",
    "tags": ["削边销", "定位", "夹具"],
    "memoryTips": "<div style='background:#dbeafe; padding:15px; border-radius:12px; border-left:4px solid #3b82f6;'><h4 style='color:#1e40af; margin-bottom:10px;'>答案解析</h4><div style='background:#bfdbfe; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0;'><p style='color:#1e3a8a; margin:0; line-height:1.8;'><strong>为什么这样答？</strong> 需要说明<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>应用场景</span>、<span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>目的</span>、<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>具体做法</span>、<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>结果</span>。</p></div><img src='images/reduced-pin.svg' style='max-width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:2px solid #3b82f6;' alt='削边销定位原理图'/><h5 style='color:#1e40af; margin:15px 0 8px;'>答案逻辑链</h5><ol style='color:#334155; margin:0; padding-left:20px; line-height:2;'><li><span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>应用场景</span>：<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>两孔定位</span></li><li><span style='background:#f472b6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>问题</span>：第二销会碰到孔壁（<span style='background:#ef4444; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>过定位</span>）</li><li><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>解决方案</span>：<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>削去</span>碰到孔壁的部分</li><li><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>目的</span>：<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>增加连心线方向的间隙</span>，避免过定位</li><li><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>结果</span>：只留下<span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>部分圆柱面</span></li></ol><div style='background:#eff6ff; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0;'><h5 style='color:#1e40af; margin:0 0 8px;'>削边销截面示意</h5><pre style='color:#1e3a8a; margin:0; font-family:monospace; font-size:14px; line-height:1.4;'>  +--------+\n /          |  <- 削去部分(间隙)\n|   圆心    |\n \\          |  <- 削去部分(间隙)\n  +--------+</pre></div><div style='background:#dbeafe; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:1px dashed #3b82f6;'><p style='color:#1e40af; margin:0;'><strong>核心理解：</strong>削边销 = <span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>两孔定位</span>时，<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>第二销削边</span>避免<span style='background:#ef4444; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>过定位</span></p></div></div>"
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "year": 2014,
    "type": "论述题",
    "question": "画出车削过程中的三个主要变形区，并简述其特点及对于加工系统的影响",
    "answer": "<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>第 I 变形区：</span><span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>基本变形区</span>，<span style='background:#fde047; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>变形量大</span>，切削层的塑性变形区常用来说明切削过程<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>变形程度</span>。\n\n<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>第 II 变形区：</span><span style='background:#f472b6; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>摩擦变形区</span>，切削与前刀面摩擦的区域切削形成后与前刀面有压力，所以沿刀面流出时有<span style='background:#ef4444; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>很大的摩擦力</span>所以切削底层又一次的发生<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>塑性变形</span>。\n\n<span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>第 III 变形区：</span><span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>加工表面变形区</span>，<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>已加工表面与后刀面接触</span>，<span style='background:#f472b6; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>影响已加工表面的加工质量</span>。",
    "tags": ["切削变形区", "车削", "切削机理"],
    "memoryTips": "<div style='background:#fce7f3; padding:15px; border-radius:12px; border-left:4px solid #ec4899;'><h4 style='color:#9d174d; margin-bottom:10px;'>答案解析</h4><div style='background:#fbcfe8; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0;'><p style='color:#831843; margin:0; line-height:1.8;'><strong>为什么这样答？</strong> 三个变形区按<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>位置</span>区分，每个区要说明<span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>特点</span>和<span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>影响</span>。</p></div><table style='width:100%; margin:15px 0; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px;'><tr style='background:#fbcfe8;'><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #ec4899;'>变形区</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #ec4899;'>位置</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #ec4899;'>核心特点</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #ec4899;'>主要影响</th></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>第I区</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>切削层</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#fde047; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>剪切滑移，变形最大</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>切削力、切屑形成</span></td></tr><tr style='background:#fdf2f8;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>第II区</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>刀-屑接触面</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>摩擦变形</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid:#f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#f472b6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>切削温度、刀具磨损</span></td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>第III区</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>刀-工接触面</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>表面变形、回弹摩擦</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #f9a8d4;'><span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>表面质量、加工硬化</span></td></tr></table><div style='background:#fce7f3; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0;'><h5 style='color:#9d174d; margin:0 0 8px;'>变形区位置示意</h5><pre style='color:#831843; margin:0; font-family:monospace; font-size:12px; line-height:1.4;'>   切屑\n    +\n工件 ->+----+<- 前刀面\n  表面 | II区 |   (摩擦区)\n       |     |\n-------+-I---+---- 剪切面\n       |     |\n       | III |   (刀-工接触)\n       +----+<- 后刀面\n     已加工表面</pre></div><div style='background:#fce7f3; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:1px dashed #ec4899;'><p style='color:#9d174d; margin:0;'><strong>记忆逻辑：</strong>按切屑流动方向：<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>I区（剪切）</span> <span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>II区（刀-屑摩擦）</span> <span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>III区（刀-工摩擦）</span></p></div></div>"
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "year": 2014,
    "type": "论述题",
    "question": "完全定位、不完全定位、过定位、欠定位四者的区别",
    "answer": "<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>完全定位：</span>在对工件进行定位支撑时<span style='background:#fde047; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>限制了工件全部六个自由度</span>的定位。\n\n<span style='background:#93c5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>不完全定位：</span>根据加工要求，工件在一个或几个方向上<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>不需要限制自由度</span>，这种<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>允许少于六点的定位</span>称为不完全定位。\n\n<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>过定位：</span>工件的某一个自由度<span style='background:#ef4444; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>同时被一个以上的定位支撑点重复限制</span>，则对这个自由度的限制会产生<span style='background:#f472b6; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>矛盾</span>，这种情况称为过定位。\n\n<span style='background:#ef4444; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>欠定位：</span>在加工中，工件的<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>定位支撑点数量少于应限制的自由度数</span>必然导致<span style='background:#ef4444; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>达不到所要求的加工精度</span>，这种定位点不足的情况称为欠定位。",
    "tags": ["定位", "自由度", "夹具"],
    "memoryTips": "<div style='background:#cffafe; padding:15px; border-radius:12px; border-left:4px solid #06b6d4;'><h4 style='color:#0e7490; margin-bottom:10px;'>答案解析</h4><div style='background:#a5f3fc; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0;'><p style='color:#155e75; margin:0; line-height:1.8;'><strong>为什么这样答？</strong> 四种定位的核心区别在于<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>限制自由度的数量</span>和<span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>方式</span>不同。</p></div><table style='width:100%; margin:15px 0; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px;'><tr style='background:#a5f3fc;'><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #22d3ee;'>定位类型</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #22d3ee;'>限制自由度</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #22d3ee;'>核心特征</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #22d3ee;'>是否允许</th></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>完全定位</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#fde047; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>6个</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>全部限制</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>正确</span></td></tr><tr style='background:#ecfeff;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#93c5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>不完全定位</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>&lt;6个</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'>加工不需要的方向不限</td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>合理</span></td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>过定位</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#ef4444; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>重复限制</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#f472b6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>一个自由度被多个点限制</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>不允许</span></td></tr><tr style='background:#ecfeff;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>欠定位</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#ef4444; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>不足</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'>限制点数少于应限自由度数</td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #67e8f9;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>不允许</span></td></tr></table><div style='background:#cffafe; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0;'><h5 style='color:#0e7490; margin:0 0 8px;'>六自由度示意</h5><pre style='color:#155e75; margin:0; font-family:monospace; font-size:12px; line-height:1.4;'>  工件\n   +Z\n   |\n  /|\\  绕X转(滚)\n / | \\ 绕Y转(俯)\n/  |  \\绕Z转(偏)\n+-------+-X\n 前后移 左右移 上下移\n  (X)   (Y)   (Z)</pre></div><div style='background:#cffafe; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:1px dashed #06b6d4;'><p style='color:#0e7490; margin:0;'><strong>判断要点：</strong>先确定需要限制几个自由度-再看实际限制几个-<span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>6个=完全</span>、<span style='background:#93c5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>&lt;6个但够用=不完全</span>、<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>重复=过定位</span>、<span style='background:#ef4444; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>不够=欠定位</span></p></div></div>"
  },
  {
    "id": 9,
    "year": 2014,
    "type": "论述题",
    "question": "确定工序加工余量时应该考虑的因素",
    "answer": "<span style='background:#fde047; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>1. 上工序的表面粗糙度</span>\n<span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>2. 上工序的表面破坏层</span>\n<span style='background:#86efac; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>3. 上工序的尺寸公差</span>\n<span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>4. 需要单独考虑的误差</span>\n<span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:4px;'>5. 本工序的安装误差</span>",
    "tags": ["加工余量", "工艺设计"],
    "memoryTips": "<div style='background:#f3e8ff; padding:15px; border-radius:12px; border-left:4px solid #a855f7;'><h4 style='color:#6b21a8; margin-bottom:10px;'>答案解析</h4><div style='background:#e9d5ff; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:10px 0;'><p style='color:#581c87; margin:0; line-height:1.8;'><strong>为什么这样答？</strong> 加工余量要足够<span style='background:#fef08a; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>去除上工序的缺陷</span>，还要<span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>补偿各种误差</span>。</p></div><img src='images/machining-allowance.svg' style='max-width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:2px solid #a855f7;' alt='加工余量示意图'/><h5 style='color:#6b21a8; margin:15px 0 8px;'>五因素分类记忆</h5><table style='width:100%; margin:10px 0; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:13px;'><tr style='background:#e9d5ff;'><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #c084fc;'>类别</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #c084fc;'>因素</th><th style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #c084fc;'>原因</th></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;' rowspan='2'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>上工序表面质量</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'><span style='background:#fde047; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>表面粗糙度</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'>要覆盖Ra值</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'><span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>表面破坏层</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'>脱碳/氧化层必须去除</td></tr><tr style='background:#faf5ff;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>上工序尺寸误差</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'><span style='background:#86efac; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>尺寸公差</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'>上工序尺寸波动范围</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'><span style='background:#c4b5fd; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>特殊误差</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'><span style='background:#f472b6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>单独考虑的误差</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'>形位误差等特殊情况</td></tr><tr style='background:#faf5ff;'><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'><span style='background:#dbeafe; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>本工序误差</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'><span style='background:#60a5fa; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;'>安装误差</span></td><td style='padding:8px; border:1px solid #d8b4fe;'>定位夹紧带来的误差</td></tr></table><div style='background:#faf5ff; padding:12px; border-radius:8px; margin:15px 0; border:1px dashed #a855f7;'><h5 style='color:#6b21a8; margin:0 0 8px;'>公式理解</h5><pre style='color:#581c87; margin:0; font-family:monospace; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6;'>最小余量 >= <span style='background:#fde047; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px;'>表面粗糙度</span> + <span style='background:#fca5a5; padding:2px 4px; border-radius:3px;'>表面破坏层</span>\n\n实际余量 = 上述5因素之和</pre></div></div>"
  }
]
